     <p>
    Talent comes from a lot of places.  Sometimes, artists can’t properly showcase their talents because they don’t have access to the necessary resources.  Progression in the entertainment sector is often confined to a network of personal connections for both artist growth and employment.  Well, things are about to change.
<br>
<br>
   We aim to level the playing field by providing resources and connections to artists nationwide, regardless of their network or location. A great work should not go unnoticed because it wasn’t made in LA or New York, and the same goes for the artists that make them.
